claim.claim-text:
A power tool battery pack comprising:
a housing having first and second walls;
at least one rechargeable battery cell disposed within the housing;
a first receiver coil disposed within the housing for receiving a magnetic field generated by a wireless charger, a voltage induced in the first receiver coil being used to charge the at least one rechargeable battery cell;
a second receiver coil disposed within the housing for receiving a magnetic field generated by the wireless charger, a voltage induced in the second receiver coil being used to charge the at least one rechargeable battery cell;
a control circuit connected to the first receiver coil for controlling the amount of power that is provided to the at least one rechargeable battery cell; and
a communication circuit connected to the control circuit for providing control information to the wireless charger;
wherein the first and second receiver coils are disposed adjacent to first and second walls, respectively.
